description: This set will attempt to accumulate ETH by being long BTC when the ETH/BTC ratio looks bearish.  This set will experience higher volatility than my ETH/cUSDC set since it will always be exposed to either ETH or BTC.  This set is based on my price action candlestick analysis.  During times there are no specific trades setups I will have the set balanced according on my long term bias.
name: ETH/BTC Price Action Candlestick Set
